desc: NurseLuxe is the #1 subscription box designed for nurses. Get your own NurseLuxe subscription, or give a box to your favorite nurse as a gift!

layout.text:
You Save Lives.
You Deserve A Present.

GET THE MOST LUXE, FUN AND COVETABLE ESSENTIALS
FOR NURSES IN ONE SUBSCRIPTION BOX!
EACH MONTH, WE SEND YOU A CURATED SET OF ITEMS 
TO USE ON AND OFF THE JOB.
